---
<div id="exit-intent-popup" class="exit-popup-overlay" aria-hidden="true" role="dialog">
  <div class="exit-popup-content">
    <button id="close-exit-popup" class="exit-popup-close" aria-label="Fermer la fenêtre">&times;</button>
    <div class="exit-popup-header">
      <span class="exit-popup-badge">💡 Opportunité Landes 40</span>
      <h2>Seniors des Landes : Ne passez pas à côté de vos aides 2026 !</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="exit-popup-body">
      <p>Le <strong>Conseil Départemental des Landes</strong> et l'Anah financent jusqu'à <strong>70% du montant</strong> de l'installation de votre monte-escalier via <strong>MaPrimeAdapt'</strong> et l'<strong>APA 40</strong>.</p>
      
      <div class="exit-popup-stats">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <span class="stat-number">25%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Crédit d'impôt direct</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <span class="stat-number">GIR 1-4</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Éligibilité APA 40</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="exit-popup-note">Simple, gratuit et sans engagement : faites estimer vos subventions en 2 minutes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exit-popup-footer">
      <a href="/devis/" class="btn-primary exit-popup-btn">Estimer mes aides &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .exit-popup-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: rgba(22, 101, 52, 0.4);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    z-index: 1000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .exit-popup-overlay.show {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  .exit-popup-content {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 35px;
    max-width: 500px;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(22, 101, 52, 0.15);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    transform: scale(0.9);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .exit-popup-overlay.show .exit-popup-content {
    transform: scale(1);
  }

  .exit-popup-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 15px;
    right: 20px;
    font-size: 28px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .exit-popup-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background-color: var(--primary-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    color: var(--primary);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .exit-popup-header h2 {
    margin-top: 15px;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .exit-popup-body {
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .exit-popup-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 15px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .stat-box {
    flex: 1;
    background-color: var(--primary-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px;
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .exit-popup-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 15px;
  }

  .exit-popup-btn {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const popup = document.getElementById('exit-intent-popup');
    const closeBtn = document.getElementById('close-exit-popup');
    const storageKey = 'monte_escalier_exit_popup_shown_40';
    
    if (!popup) return;
    
    // Check if already shown
    const isShown = localStorage.getItem(storageKey);
    if (isShown) return;
    
    const showPopup = () => {
      popup.classList.add('show');
      popup.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'false');
      localStorage.setItem(storageKey, 'true');
    };
    
    // Desktop: exit intent on mouseleave top of window
    document.addEventListener('mouseleave', (e) => {
      if (e.clientY < 50) {
        showPopup();
      }
    });
    
    // Mobile: trigger after 20s
    setTimeout(() => {
      const isMobile = window.innerWidth <= 768;
      if (isMobile) {
        showPopup();
      }
    }, 20000);

    // Close actions
    const closePopup = () => {
      popup.classList.remove('show');
      popup.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
    };

    if (closeBtn) {
      closeBtn.addEventListener('click', closePopup);
    }

    popup.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      if (e.target === popup) {
        closePopup();
      }
    });
  });
</script>
